WEBVTT

00:01.599 --> 00:04.162
In Northern Italy, in the foothills of the Alps,...

00:04.903 --> 00:07.707
...a collection of temples dedicated to the human spirit...

00:08.181 --> 00:10.126
...sit 100 feet below ground.

00:14.313 --> 00:16.955
Built in secret over a period of 15 years,...

00:17.595 --> 00:20.611
...this is Damanhur, the Temples of Humankind.

